 Ability of using computer to do mathematics.
□ 應用隨機理論的能力
 Ability to apply stochastic mathematics.
□ 處理大量數據的能力
 Ability to handle large amount of data.
□ 處理離散型數學的能力
 Ability to do mathematics relating to discrete models.
□ 獨立研究的能力
 Ability to do independent studies of mathematics.
□ 使用計算機的能力
 Abilities to use computer as a tool.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       這門課主要是介紹基本的複變數函數的理論。主要的內容包括複數系、解析函數、初等函數、複數積分、解析函數的數列表示、留數理論、保角映射以及 Fourier 和 Laplace 轉換。除了基礎理論，我們也將簡單介紹一些在物理或工程方面的應用。This course provides the mathematical foundations needed for understanding and working with the modern analysis. The main topics are complex number system, analytic functions, integrations, conformal mappings and some integral transformations. Some applications in physics and engineering will also be included.     

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Be familiar with the analyticity and the Cauch-Riemann Equations. Be familiar with properties of analytic functions. Be familiar with the residue theorem. 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Complex Numbers and Functions of Complex Variable z2Complex Numbers and Functions of Complex Variable z3Analytic Functions4Line Integrals and Entire Functions 5Properties of Entire Functions 6Properties of Analytic Functions 7Further Properties of Analytic Functions 8Midterm Exam9Simply Connected Domains10Isolated Singularities of an Analytic Function11The Residue Theorem12The Residue Theorem and Applications of the Residue Theorem13The Residue Theorem and Applications of the Residue Theorem14Further Contour Integral Techniques15Introduction to Conformal Mapping16Introduction to Conformal Mapping17The Riemann Mapping Theorem18Final Exam 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


